  m_text: 'Controls:

    1. WASD - Move

    2. Right Shift  - Sprint

    3. Change
    Gravity - Hold(Right Mouse) & Tap(E) while facing desired direction

    4. Shoot(Left
    Mouse)

    5. Reload(R)

    6. Talk with Companion(1 or 2)

    7. Clear Companion
    dialog (0)

    8. Return to Main Menu (Escape)

    9. Return to HubWorld (H)'
